OhMyREPL

This is my REPL. There are many like it, but this one is mine.

This is the documentation for OhMyREPL; a Julia package that hooks into the Julia REPL and gives it new features.

A video showing installation and features of the package is available here but note that a few things (including the name of the package) has changed since the video was made.
